/*********************************************************************/
/*      LafortuneMaterial                                            */
/*********************************************************************/

Lafotune Model:
----------------

The Lafortune BRDF model is a simple but yet very powerful BRDF model.
This OpenSG Material allows to render objects with this model, instead
of the simple Phong model. Furthermore a diffuse texture can be set
(or a combined diffuse/specular texture). 

Characteristics:
-------------------

1. Use Vertex Program and (ARB Fragment Program or NVIDIA Register Combiners)
   for shading. User can choose FP or RC mode.
2. Possible to add a texture for the diffuse term. (If the
   texture not needed, use white texture)
3. Vertex and Fragment Programs are embedded in the code.

